dict.string: Dr. Molly Ann Timmerman, D.O. has 1 year of experience and practices in Physical Medicine and Rehabilitation

Dr. Timmerman graduated from Western University of Health Sciences, Pomona, California. She has 3 hospital affiliations at Palo Alto Veterans Affairs Medical Center, San Mateo Medical Center and Stanford Medical Center.
Dr. Timmerman is board certified in Physical Medicine and Rehabilitation. She has special expertise in 3 areas, including musculoskeletal medicine, traumatic brain injury, and amputee care.
